WEBVTT

00:00:00.437 --> 00:00:02.452
Track 07.07

00:00:04.226 --> 00:00:05.357
Shop Assistant: Can I help you?

00:00:05.833 --> 00:00:06.825
Customer: Yes,

00:00:07.163 --> 00:00:09.663
how much are these white plates?

00:00:09.762 --> 00:00:11.666
Shop Assistant: They’re £4 each.

00:00:11.786 --> 00:00:12.619
Customer: OK,

00:00:12.798 --> 00:00:15.199
I’d like four white plates, please.

00:00:15.279 --> 00:00:16.052
Shop Assistant: Certainly.

00:00:16.211 --> 00:00:18.434
That’s £16, please.

00:00:18.652 --> 00:00:20.576
Customer: Can I use a card to pay?

00:00:20.775 --> 00:00:22.084
Shop Assistant: Of course.

00:00:22.243 --> 00:00:23.907
Enter your PIN, please.

00:00:24.650 --> 00:00:26.905
OK, here’s your receipt.

00:00:27.202 --> 00:00:28.591
Would you like a bag?

00:00:28.671 --> 00:00:30.158
Customer: No, don’t worry.

00:00:30.258 --> 00:00:32.301
Shop Assistant: OK, here you are.

00:00:32.401 --> 00:00:33.829
Customer: Thank you very much.

00:00:33.909 --> 00:00:34.762
Shop Assistant: Thank you.